Paula is a panda, longing to climb as many trees as possible. 
You need to help take care of Paula so she can spend moentre time climbing trees. 
If the green light is on, Paula is happy and content in life. 
However, after ____{enter time speriod} Paula's red light will start to flash which makes the red light flash. 
If this happens, press the heart to give Paula her medicine. When the medicine works the blue light(food) and yellow medicine light should begin to flash and the green light will eventually come on.
